title: Naval Sports Complex (Pakistan)
text: Naval Sports Complex is a multi-use <a href="stadium">stadium</a> in <a href="Islamabad">Islamabad</a>. It is mostly used for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> games and is the home of <a href="Pakistan%20Navy%20FC">Pakistan Navy FC</a>. The stadium has the capacity to hold 1,000 people.
